To install the library you should do the following steps:

> make
> sudo make install

To test the library with a factorial program, run:

> make factorial
> ./factorial

And try to compute the factorial of some big number. For additional help on how to use the library download the user manual from our webpage in google code:

http://code.google.com/p/in-silico/

This library is distributed with Apache 2 Licence. The creators of the library are from InSilico group of Universidad Tecnologica de Pereira (Colombia)
